539
00:30:03,736 --> 00:30:07,522
Because it upsets me. All I ever wanted for you was a normal life.

540
00:30:07,766 --> 00:30:08,660
Why, mom?

541
00:30:08,968 --> 00:30:10,373
Why is normal so good?

542
00:30:11,085 --> 00:30:12,820
My life is fascinating.

543
00:30:13,278 --> 00:30:16,122
It's extraordinary. I found a way to really help people.

544
00:30:16,555 --> 00:30:18,490
Why can't you just be happy about that?

545
00:30:18,496 --> 00:30:19,493
She can't, Melinda.

546
00:30:20,628 --> 00:30:21,843
