557
00:30:44,796 --> 00:30:46,031
Right. Um,

558
00:30:47,215 --> 00:30:50,113
well, you wanna talk to your mom and dad together, right?

559
00:30:50,807 --> 00:30:52,402
Uh, your dad might be hurt

560
00:30:52,968 --> 00:30:55,313
