574
00:31:32,298 --> 00:31:33,190
Your mother...

575
00:31:34,415 --> 00:31:37,060
I've never seen a woman more in love with her child.

576
00:31:37,176 --> 00:31:38,673
Unless, of course, it was me.

577
00:31:39,818 --> 00:31:42,761
We would sit there staring at the two of you in amazement.

578
00:31:42,956 --> 00:31:45,043
So perfect, so beautiful.

579
00:31:46,358 --> 00:31:47,503
