595
00:32:38,575 --> 00:32:41,441
How could I survive the thing that killed my little girl?

596
00:32:41,447 --> 00:32:43,890
Yeah, but you have your whole life ahead of you.

597
00:32:43,927 --> 00:32:45,280
You know, for some people,

598
00:32:45,855 --> 00:32:48,052
Melinda, that's not particularly good news.

599
