686
00:37:37,925 --> 00:37:39,210
I want you to stay here

687
00:37:40,467 --> 00:37:41,363
with daddy.

688
00:37:41,918 --> 00:37:42,913
She wants you to...

689
00:37:44,107 --> 00:37:45,002
